Portfolio Models Structure
==========================

Before (1 large file):
----------------------
portfolio_model.dart (423 lines)
  └── All 7 models in one file

After (Clean separation):
------------------------
models/
├── models.dart (8 lines) ...................... [BARREL FILE - Import this!]
├── portfolio_model.dart (105 lines) ........... Main portfolio model
├── social_link.dart (27 lines) ................ Social media links
├── project.dart (73 lines) .................... Projects
├── skill.dart (38 lines) ...................... Skills
├── course.dart (57 lines) ..................... Courses
├── experience.dart (65 lines) ................. Work experience
└── education.dart (66 lines) .................. Education

Benefits:
---------
✅ Each model has its own file
✅ Easy to find and maintain
✅ Better code organization
✅ Follows single responsibility principle
✅ Clean imports via barrel file

Usage:
------
// Import all models at once
import 'package:portfolio/models/models.dart';

// Now use any model
final portfolio = PortfolioModel(...);
final project = Project(...);
final skill = Skill(...);

